Text: Is there no end to this memory?
For a mercy, its movements were easy to read.
I'm sure this was a beautiful castle once...
Such tragedy was commonplace during the Contramemoria...
Who could be behind all this?
Such carnage. Such cruelty. This is...
We must find a way across.
That he should place such faith in Golbez...
Let us leave the other side to him.
In any case, it would be rude of us not to respond in kind.
They've all but brought the Final Days upon themselves.
He gave himself to the Dark to stop Golbez...
It seems we've no choice but to fight...
And yet it falls to us to keep him─or rather, you─from harm.
Drown them and be done with it!
I can't take any more of his pestering.
How could something so large move so quickly!?
I try to only speak kindly of others, but they test me...
I try to only speak kindly of others, but they test me...
So many regulators... They all used to belong to someone...
Not the best camouflage, now is it?
Ahaha, so only intruders can bust in through the front!
The conveyor's been activated. We can continue up.
Looks like they knew we were coming...
This won't be comfortable, but intruders can't be choosers.
They're headed up...but where do we go from here?
This has the look of a research laboratory...
I'm going to become a knight and protect the princess!
“Service Eternal”... She truly lives by her words.
We all of us must do our part for the kingdom.
Blessings be upon you, Your Highness!
It's so uplifting just to see and hear Her Highness.
Even with all her duties, she makes time for us.
That's the spirit! They'll be inviting us to join a caravan any day now!
We'll find help! Stay strong until we return!
Incredible! Oh, thank the gods it didn't reach the village...
Our community is in your debt!
We've made good progress. What say we rest here?
Fine by me. I'm sure our alpacas would appreciate a break.
Hmm... Perhaps we overfilled our wagons this trip.
Nonsense! Think of the profits we'll rake in when we get there!
Huh? What's gotten into them all of a sudden?
Thank you so much for driving them off.
Now to get these supplies home!
Perhaps we'll see you around sometime.
Leave them! Our lives take precedence over profit!
How terrified you must have been...
We won't give up, Your Majesty!
It's not over till it's over!
Feel the sting of my blade!
They say over a thousand people died here!
Hear what? A ghost? Everyone knows there's no such thing as─
Sorry, I'll get out of your way!
If the glyphs are lost, our ancestors will die!
We must repair them at once.
Excellent work. The wind sprites have settled.
Thanks to you, the glyphs are undamaged.
Now we need but hope the Stormrider won't show itself.
It appears I spoke too soon! Save yourself, outsider!
To protect my family, I shall bring my all to bear!
Ahhh... A dip in the hot springs is just what I needed.
Soothing, isn't it? I feel so...toasty!
You know, this could be our final moment alive...
Oh, please. That old wives' tale doesn't scare me.
Gods help me─the Pelu eater is real!?

Scythe in hand, into the fray,
Sally is here to sweep you away!

Dust and dirt, muck and grime,
this is where Sally draws the line!
So much for a tranquil boat ride!
I can't command the punutiy like this...
Seems Bakool Ja Ja got his way...

We have to mend this damage.
If you could help me, Alisaie...?
None can compare to the Resilient Son!
The First Promise was born to sit the throne!
He will be a great Dawnservant!
Come along, Pana! It's time for a stroll!
Gotta keep our legs strong if we want to join a caravan!
Souls are being extracted from regulators...
The glowing things─they're souls, all of them.
According to Elene'shpya, we continue through here.
The souls are being cleansed prior to storage...
I see... This is where they researched the use of feral souls!
Haha! You're no match for our magitek!
With the blessing, how can we lose?
Th-There's nothing to be afraid of!
I can do this... I know I can!
Keep this up, and we'll soon be rolling in riches!
Your days of ruling the roost are over!
I can't take this any longer!
Aaagh! I'm not cut out for this!
I just want to go home!
Shoo! That's my harvest, you feathered freaks!
I must preserve the stonework somehow...
Behold power of Tural's true rulers!
We bring our all to bear!
Ha! We are true rulers of Tural!
Puny outsider never stood a chance!
Know the true power of Chirwagur!
We will always be rightful rulers of Tural!
Defeated? No, tactical retreat! You'll pay for this!
Leave everythin' you have and get outta sight!
Still got some fight left, huh?
These organisms pose a threat to the district's ecosystem.
Hostile organisms exterminated. Disengaging combat protocols.
We have suffered extensive damage. The threat cannot be contained.
I require urgent assistance. A large number of foraging organisms have been sighted in this district.
Seeds of the rarer plants must be recovered before irreparable damage is done to the ecosystem in Windspath Gardens.
I require assistance to gather enough seeds before they are consumed.
The requisite number of seeds has been delivered. I thank you for your assistance.
We were unable to gather a sufficient number of seeds. A more efficient strategy must be formed.
Witnesss the wrath of we three heads!
If three heads do not sssuffice, you shall face the ssstrength of sssix!
We heads hunger! You will regret thisss intrusion!
Purging contaminated organisms before flow of water is affected.
Present conditions pose a threat to the canals. Requesting assistance...
Massive organism detected. Extermination will commence.
Source of the contamination is unclear. Requesting assistance...
We are unable to purge the contaminants at our current strength. Making a temporary retreat.
Massive contaminant sighted. Extermination will commence immediately.
Massive contaminant contained. Thank you for aiding us in our mission.
Chances of mission success are nominal. Retreating.
Please stand clear. Please stand clear.
Warning. Resources have escaped. Moving to recapture.
Oho! I'll soon be reeling a whopper!
Come on, fishies... Just one bite is all I need.
Run for your life! It's mistaken us for bait!
My poor reeds and their poor roots...
I beg of you, rid my reeds of those pests!
Blessings of great serpent upon us!
This is land of the Chirwagur!
Stay away from the sacred vessel!
The great serpent must not be awakened!
Conducting a search of the area. Requesting friendly escort.
I will be bound no more!
Still alive, I see! Then play a game with me─the very last one of your lives!
You like cards, don't you? Everyone likes cards! Remember the numbers on each one─if you forget in the game, you die in real life!
The number of acorns will decide your fate. Remember them, or else!
It's time to draw a card! Fire up those tired brains of yours!
Now, which card did I draw first? Choose wisely, for your lives depend on it!
Oh my! Survivors!? Well then, that means it's time to draw even more cards!
Here I go! I wonder what I'll draw first?
And finally, the third one! What do you think it'll be?
Do you remember which card I drew first? Or are your wits as slow as your feet?
Which card did I draw second? If you tire of living, wrong answers are gladly accepted!
What was the third card again? I honestly can't remember!
Hooray for those still alive! You get to be amazed by my balancing act!
Don't get hit, unless you're a glutton for pain!
Has everyone gained a new appreciation for life? Honestly, I'd rather you were dead!
Now watch the rings carefully! Everyone deserves to see something beautiful during their final moments!
As much as it pains me to see anyone left alive, I must bid you farewell! Perhaps your future adventures will give you the fate I couldn't!
Unit identification: GX-0090. Commencing patrol of Canal Town.
Large numbers of aggressive torbalans have been sighted in the district. We ask that external support prioritize protection of our patrol at all costs.
The torbalans have been driven back. With no threat remaining, we will return to our regular patrol.
Unable to proceed with our patrol under current conditions. We must develop another strategy...
\<bleep> ErRoR... Initiating system reboot. Preparing to relay today's weather report...
Acquiring meteorological data... Get ready for a fun, fun forecast!
Expect a sizzling salvo of scorching sunshine and arid air. Perfect wildfire conditions!
Prepare for a high-voltage bout of booming thunder. A hyperelectric phenomenon!
Brace yourself for a pane-shattering tempest of epic proportions. Gale-force winds incoming!
I forecast frozen fiends and sparkling snowscapes. Don your mittens for blizzard conditions!
We're due a drenching deluge no umbrella could withstand. Prepare for flood conditions!
Reacquiring data... Searing sunshine will give way to electric storms, followed by the coldest of cold snaps!
Reacquiring data... Thunderclouds will give way to ferocious gales then sizzling heat!
Reacquiring data... Blinding blizzards will turn to lightning storms, followed by tremendous gales!
Reacquiring data... A howling tempest will stoke raging wildfires, followed by an almighty snowstorm!
\<bleep> \<bloop>! Adjusting weather in line with predictions!
We should be able to complete our patrol of Canal Town without further incident. Thank you for your help this day.
I do hope these offerings stay safe...
But I fear the scent will attract a fiend or two.
Oh, no... Toucalibri! We must hold them off!
Damaged sentries have been discovered in this area. Requesting support...
